Class FoodItem

java.lang.Object
foms.food.FoodItem
All Implemented Interfaces:
Serializable
Direct Known Subclasses:
Drinks, MainDish, SetMeal, Sides
public abstract class FoodItem extends Object implements Serializable
Represents a food item in the menu, providing methods to customize and manage its properties.
